Package com.smartgwt.client.bean

Interface Summary
BeanFactory.CanvasMetaFactory Interface used to trigger the generation and registration of reflection metadata for Canvas and all its subclasses found in the classpath (including your custom subclasses).
BeanFactory.FormItemMetaFactory Interface used to trigger the generation and registration of reflection metadata for FormItem and all its subclasses found in the classpath (including your custom subclasses).
BeanFactory.MetaFactory An interface which you can extend in order to register classes with the BeanFactory reflection mechanism.
BeanValueType.MetaFactory Interface used to trigger the generation and registration of reflection metadata for argument types.
